na, comenzando con las intervenciones de la Internacional Comunista. Se examina si este legado también ha influido en los protagonistas del »progresismo« y de qué manera. La reflexión en la parte principal se basa en el papel central de Hugo Chávez y su relación ambivalente con la herencia histórica de la izquierda.  afunded by BMBF  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/4.0 uhttp://www.transcript-verlag.de/open-access-bei-transcript  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCommunismzLatin America. 0aPolitical violencezLatin America. 0aRegime change. 4aAmerika. 4aAmérica Latina. 4aBielefeld University Press. 4aLateinamerika. 4aLeninismo. 4aPolitik. 4aPolitische Soziologie. 4aPolitisches System. 4aProgresismo. 4aStalinismo. 4aSüdamerikanische Geschichte. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / History & Theory.2bisacsh  aAmerica.  aBielefeld University Press.  aPolitical Sociology.  aPolitical System.  aPolitics.  aSouth American History.2 aBMBFefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Political Science 2021z9783110753943oZDB-23-PLW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839456415zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839456415zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839456415/original  a978-3-11-074335-7 DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-GOA  aZDB-23-PLWb2021